10:T437,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"TVSeries","name":"And you thought there is never a girl online?","description":"The story centers on Hideki Nishimura, a young man who confessed to a person he thought was a girl online, only for that person to turn out to be a boy. He keeps this \"black history\" secret and swears to never to trust a \"girl\" online again. However, one day a girl online confesses to him, and it turns out she's actually a beautiful girl named Ako Tamaki. Ako cannot tell the difference between the online world and reality, and she is a loner who has trouble communicating. Hideki and his friends from his guild decide to work together to \"correct\" her.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)","image":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx21290-R6qYWnylwpbL.png","datePublished":"2016-04-07","numberOfEpisodes":12,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","inLanguage":"ja","genre":["Comedy","Ecchi","Romance"],"aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":6.3,"bestRating":10,"ratingCount":0}}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$10"}}],["$","$L11",null,{"initialDrama":{"id":"08987597-995f-4164-b074-767694faad6a","tmdb_id":21290,"imdb_id":null,"content_type":"anime","title":"And you thought there is never a girl online?","original_title":"ネトゲの嫁は女の子じゃないと思った?","overview":"The story centers on Hideki Nishimura, a young man who confessed to a person he thought was a girl online, only for that person to turn out to be a boy. He keeps this \"black history\" secret and swears to never to trust a \"girl\" online again. However, one day a girl online confesses to him, and it turns out she's actually a beautiful girl named Ako Tamaki. Ako cannot tell the difference between the online world and reality, and she is a loner who has trouble communicating. Hideki and his friends from his guild decide to work together to \"correct\" her.\n<br><br>\n(Sou